  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove the lamb from the pot and set it aside.",
    "Add the onion to the pot and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the Thai chilli jam and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef broth, tomato paste, and red wine vinegar to the pot.",
    "Return the lamb to the pot and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Transfer the pot to the oven and braise the lamb for 2 hours, or until tender.",
    "Season the stew with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley if desired."
